{"tid":370690,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"會唔會真係悶到死咗","createTime":"2017-08-23T07:15:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-23T08:29:29.000Z","uid":117790,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6cf53b456e44be8c19adce0168b5ce4126d4f8b2","tid":370690,"uid":117790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T07:15:37.000Z","msg":"返工好悶，喺屋企又好悶。冇嘢做又唔想煲劇，個人又冇興趣，又冇朋友。想出街行吓，去吓沙灘，去吓郊外都冇人陪。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n悶到好撚辛苦，其實我會唔會有日真係悶死咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f451e705ab6bf0a9124ebf7dba75c0c03fbe8ccf","tid":370690,"uid":64781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T07:25:51.000Z","msg":"join 下興趣班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00c2e114a40005ecd6f53f307095f33715380e4b","tid":370690,"uid":117790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T07:36:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>join 下興趣班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n遲啲開學又冇時間，又冇錢，個人又易攰... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"644748676fea0bbecacde69aedc7c295d8fc4d02","tid":370690,"uid":89709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T07:47:03.000Z","msg":"係會悶死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n五月有單新聞話有個人生活枯燥就自殺左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6d521e937517dc0c804779b50a782a81fbbd806","tid":370690,"uid":117790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T07:49:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係會悶死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n五月有單新聞話有個人生活枯燥就自殺左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我悶到個人混混沌沌咁，好辛